          "tempoGroove": "Felt tempo 60–80 BPM in half-time (often written 120–160 with rolling hi-hats doubling and tripling above the slow snare). Word density is the lowest-per-bar of the modern siblings: short clipped phrases with real dead air between them, and heavy repetition doing melodic work.",
